# Session capture coverage across the fleet

Read-only reconnaissance performed on 2026-07-12 from `flagg`. Scope is
Pi, Claude Code, and Codex on `flagg`, `blaine`, and `panda`. The only mutation
was writing this requested report. No service, index, config, transcript, or
remote machine was changed.

## Coverage matrix

“Raw/day” is JSONL files modified in the last seven days divided by seven.
This is the best available session-volume proxy, but a long-lived transcript
can cross the window boundary. “Tokens/day” is source-reported usage on flagg
(including cache reads), and JSONL bytes ÷ 4 on blaine/panda. The latter is a
coarse sizing estimate, not provider billing. “Indexed freshness” is the newest
matching `runs_dev.started_at`; ✅ means current on 2026-07-12, ⚠ means raw data
is newer than the index, and ❌ means no indexed run in the last seven days.

| Machine | Surface | Raw transcript path and naming | Capture mechanism observed | Indexed freshness | Raw/day | Rough tokens/day |
|---|---|---|---|---:|---:|---:|
| flagg | Pi | `~/.pi/agent/sessions/<cwd>/ISO_<uuid>.jsonl` | Pi `memory-capture` extension → Central `/api/runs` | ✅ 2026-07-12 21:47Z | 55.9 | 313.9M incl. cache |
| flagg | Claude | `~/.claude/projects/<cwd>/<uuid>.jsonl` | Claude `Stop` hook → `joelclaw-capture-session.ts` | ✅ 2026-07-12 21:46Z | 45.0 | 247.5M incl. cache |
| flagg | Codex | `~/.codex/sessions/YYYY/MM/DD/rollout-ISO-<uuid>.jsonl` | Codex capture script/log exists; delivery not current | ⚠ 2026-06-21 16:32Z; raw current | 9.7 | 7.8M |
| blaine | Pi | same Pi layout | Pi `memory-capture`; fresh successful capture log | ✅ 2026-07-12 21:47Z | 12.0 | ~3.24M |
| blaine | Claude | same Claude layout | Claude hook/capture path; fresh index | ✅ 2026-07-12 20:05Z | 6.4 | ~4.25M |
| blaine | Codex | same Codex layout | hook runs but reports missing session/path | ⚠ 2026-06-07 21:01Z; raw 2026-07-12 | 0.4 | ~0.25M |
| panda | Pi | same Pi layout | no current capture extension observed | ❌ 2026-06-22 23:53Z | 0 | 0 |
| panda | Claude | same Claude layout | Claude remains active locally; Central/index stale | ⚠ 2026-06-23 00:57Z; raw 2026-07-12 | 0.1 | ~0.62M |
| panda | Codex | same Codex layout | no current delivery observed | ❌ 2026-06-21 16:34Z | 0 | 0 |

